div class="modal #{request.path.match(/privacy-policy/) && "is-active"}"
  .modal-background
  .modal-card
    header.modal-card-head.has-text-centered
      p.modal-card-title PRIVACY POLICY
    section.modal-card-body
      .content.is-medium
        ol
          li We only store information for the purpose of providing and maintening our service, including your name, your shipping address, your orders, your Telegram ID.

          li Your personal data may be transferred to computers and services outside of your jurisdiction, including, but not limited to France, United Kingdom, Canada and the United States.

          li By uploading content on <strong>#{Rails.configuration.site_name}</strong>, you grant us permission to use and alter this content for the sole purpose of providing our service (e.g. to crop and resize images).

          li We do not share or sell your information to third parties unrelated to the service we provide. Your shipping information and orders will be shared with <strong>Prodigi</strong> and your payment information will be shared with <strong>Stripe</strong>.

          li We do not use tracking cookies.

          li Your information is treated and stored securely, your Telegram information and your shipping address are encrypted and the service runs in isolated containers.

    footer.modal-card-foot.has-text-centered
      = link_to root_path, class: "button"
        | Close


