      p.modal-card-title TERMS AND CONDITIONS
    section.modal-card-body
      .content.is-medium
        ol
          li You must be aged 18 or older to use <strong>#{Rails.configuration.site_name}</strong>.

          li You agree not to use any material that are forbidden under French, Canadian and Welsh law or under the law of your local jurisdiction.

          li Once an order is paid and accepted by our partners its execution starts immediately.

          li Since our product are heavily customized you do not benefit from the right to retract.

          li Please remember that the quality of our products is limited by the quality and resolution of your Telegram stickers.

    footer.modal-card-foot.has-text-centered
      = link_to root_path, class: "button"
        | Close